"programme&nbsp;?</a>"

#. type: Content of: <ul><li>
msgid ""
"<a href=\"#LGPLJava\" name=\"TOCLGPLJava\">How does the LGPL work with Java?"
"</a>"
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"#LGPLJava\" name=\"TOCLGPLJava\">Comment la LGPL fonctionne-t-elle "
"avec Java&nbsp;?</a>"

